Notice the comma that separates the reporting phrase from the sentence?

Mr Tang responded, "That would be frightening."
"The Vice President is resigning", her publicist has announced.

"The cameras show Arthur had been asleep while driving", police reported.

"Mr Tang, stated" all rooms in our top hotels are fully booked.
